                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>gentleman who have taken up for one or<lb/> the other respectively.\n                                        An attempt has been<lb/> and will be made, I fear, to bring\n                                        the<lb/> matter before the congregation in which<lb/> the\n                                        friends of <persName>mr P</persName> have a numerical<lb/>\n                                        majority. His opinions however are not<lb/> held in\n                                        reverence <hi rend=\"underline\">now</hi>, by what I\n                                        consider<lb/> the best and most intelligent portion of<lb/>\n                                        our members. These last, will sustain <persName>Dr<lb/>\n                                                  Eckman</persName> who is independent, and\n                                        inclined<lb/> to orthodoxy.  </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yrs very Respflly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">T. J. Moise</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
